folder: Church Street & Franklin Street, Manhattan, NY
text:
(1)
Church Street, west side, north from and including Franklin, to and including White Streets. Also shown (across clearance for Sixth Ave., Extension), is White Street, at and adjoining the N.W. corner of Church Street.
September 12, 1927.

P. L. Sperr.

(2)
The same, a closer view.
September 12, 1927.

P. L. Sperr.
